PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1: What's the best BBQ in Nashville? The College World Series. Moving from blue states to red states. Biden: If you want to overthrow the government, you need nukes. Biden is like Milton from Office Space. Biden and Democrats know defund the police is a losing issue, try to blame increase in crime on guns. Susan Rice plays word games on defund the police. Callers on guns and crime.
